data.description: This spacious and adorable 3 bedroom, 2 bathroom home is situated on a large lot in a quiet cul-de-sac, providing plenty of privacy and space for your family to grow. Enjoy your morning coffee on the charming front porch or host a summer barbeque on the expansive back patio surrounded by a privacy fence. The cozy living room features a beautiful fireplace, perfect for snuggling up on chilly nights. With no homeowners association to worry about, you can enjoy all the benefits of homeownership without any extra fees. Park your boat or RV in the backyard under the carport and take advantage of the extra storage shed in the back. Only 2 minutes from the new Central Creek Park offering a very impressive kids park, pickle ball courts and more.  Take and afternoon stroll around the huge pond
